Evaluation Approach (Proxy, No Gold Labels)
We used detector-based proxy evaluation because only original and redacted DOCX files were available.
Entities were detected in original and redacted texts and compared by normalized entity text per type.
TP: original entity removed in redacted output.
FN: original entity still present after redaction.
FP: entity newly detected in redacted output (possible artifact/over-redaction).
Metrics are proxy estimates, not gold-span exact scores.

PII Type           |   TP |   FP |   FN | Precision |    Recall |  Accuracy
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
